playstore_details.title: SecureGuard OTP
playstore_details.description:
SecureGuard OTP (SGOTP) is an one-time-password (OTP) generator designed for SecureGuard products, e.g. SecureGuard AM, SecureGuard PM. 

SecureGuard is an access control and auditing solution which ensures security and management efficiency for accesses to all systems in a network such as servers, networks, security systems, mainframes etc. through a single gateway.

Integrating OTP with the basic SecureGuard solution, a highly secure operating environment can be built . SecureGuard  OTP does not only strengthen the security while log-in, but also in server access controls and command controls. In SecureGuard, you can set different security policies with OTP.

For more details, please visit the following website:
http://www.sgni.co.kr
